    "summary": {
      "value": "Gain bonuses with daggers and treat them as brawling, sword, and thrown weapons."
    },
    "description": "<blockquote>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>Requirements:</strong> </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">you must have mastered one or more Classes among </span><strong><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Rogue </span></strong><span class=\"fontstyle2\">and </span><strong><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Weaponmaster</span></strong><span class=\"fontstyle2\">.</span></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">While you have one or more </span><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>melee dagger</strong> </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">weapons equipped, you gain a +1 bonus to Defense and Magic Defense, and you treat those weapons as also belonging to the </span><strong><span class=\"fontstyle0\">brawling</span></strong><span class=\"fontstyle2\">, </span><strong><span class=\"fontstyle0\">sword</span></strong><span class=\"fontstyle2\">, and </span><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>thrown</strong> </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">Categories for the purpose of Skills and effects. </span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">Additionally, your attacks with weapons that belong to the </span><strong><span class=\"fontstyle0\">dagger </span></strong><span class=\"fontstyle2\">Category may target creatures that cannot normally be targeted by </span><strong><span class=\"fontstyle0\">melee </span></strong><span class=\"fontstyle2\">attacks.</span> </p>",
